    "Evaluation PhaseIn the evaluation phase, detailed in Algorithm 2, the trained agent's ability to generalize its learned behavior to new scenarios is assessed.",
    "The evaluation consists of multiple episodes, where in each episode, the agent:1.",
    "Predicts an action based on its current state.2.",
    "Executes the action in the environment and observes the resultant reward and state.3.",
    "An episode ends either when a collision is detected or when no new rewards are achieved."
